    "VPNeo routes all DNS queries through the VPN tunnel using secure DNS servers (1.1.1.1, 8.8.8.8). The Kill Switch feature adds extra protection by blocking traffic outside the tunnel." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
